    {
      "heading": "20v20 Crystal League Battles",
      "description": "With Guild Season 11, 20v20 Crystal Realm battles will be available with their own seasonal league.",
      "items": [
        "Levels 1 and 2 20v20 tokens can be bought at the Energy Manipulator for 150,000 and 300,000 Silver respectively",
        "The signup process and match schedule follow a similar pattern to the 5v5 League",
        "Matches follow rules similar to former 20v20 city fights",
        "Level 1: daily at 01:00, 12:00 and 19:00 (non-lethal)",
        "Level 2: daily at 01:30, 12:30 and 19:30 (full loot from Lv.2)",
        "Level 3: every Saturday and Sunday at specified times",
        "Level 4: every second weekend",
        "Level 5: 3 Saturdays during the season",
        "Level 6 final match occurs last Saturday"
      ],
      "searchable_text": "20v20 Crystal League Battles Season 11 tokens schedule matches levels",
      "subsections": []
    },
    {
      "heading": "Crystal League Season Points",
      "description": "Season Points for mid-level Crystal League matches have been reduced and daily limits introduced.",
      "items": [
        "Level 3: 25 → 15",
        "Level 4: 75 → 40",
        "Level 5: 200 → 100",
        "Level 6: 500 → 250",
        "Level 7: 1000 → 600",
        "Level 8: 2500 → 1600",
        "Daily limits now apply to Season Points",
        "Limits for 5v5 and 20v20 are separate"
      ],
      "searchable_text": "Crystal League Season Points daily limits level changes",
      "subsections": []
    },
    {
